rComments: Mike was a cool guy. You learned in his class even if you didn't know it. Was VERY laid back, and was willing to accommodate if necessary. CMN 323 is a good class to take if you need an A and like to debate. (More so the first.)
Awesome TA! Though he's lenient and an easy grader, you still learn a lot. Very laidback but highly intelligent too!
i liked his class. just do your work and you'll get an A
he's a pretty easy TA, you can persuade him to push back due dates. pretty easy grader too.
